":guilabel:`Sistema`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/qgis_configuration.rst:1406
msgid ""
"launching QGIS at a command prompt with the following command line ``qgis "
"--nocustomization``"
msgstr ""
"lanciando QGIS al prompt dei comandi con la seguente riga di comando ``qgis "
"--nocustomization``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/qgis_configuration.rst:1408
msgid ""
"setting to ``false`` the value of :menuselection:`UI --> Customization --> "
